rows.label: tlk70000004_03_msg0001
rows.name:
That Zain fellow doesn't look like
much, but it seems he's made us a
shelter with some impressive facilities.

rows.label: tlk70000004_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Explosion-, fire- and earthquake-proof,
and it's designed not to collapse
under its own weight.

rows.label: tlk70000004_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Next we need to worry about
food, medicine stockpiles, air
filtering and the like...

rows.label: tlk70000004_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But I don't think we need to worry
too much. Soon Iiran technological
might will surpass even Superbia's.

rows.label: tlk70000004_03_msg0005
rows.name:
And if there's anything we can't handle
ourselves, we can ask the palace
engineers. They'll be able to help.
